<PageTitle>Local username accounts</PageTitle>

<h3>Local username accounts</h3>

<p>PZ Server Launcher does not use email for account management.</p>
<p>Use <strong>Account / Manage / ChangePassword</strong> to change your own password after signing in, or ask the local owner to assign a temporary password if you are locked out.</p>
